data.description: This beautiful town home is located in a well kept and conveniently located area, just off Hwy 17 in Jacksonville! Minutes to shopping, dining and intestate 295. 3 Upstairs Bedrooms, with 2 full baths and an additional living space. Down stairs features an open floor plan with a conveniently located 1/2 bath, right as you enter the front door. The under stairs storage area, indoor laundry area and the designated back patio space are a few more +++ to this move in ready home!
